      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks but hotlines dont really help with the fact that i've just failed. everything i do feels pointless. i look at my life and there's nothing left. it's like i've been running on empty for years and now that he's gone, there's just no reason to keep running. i just want to close my eyes and let everything stop.",
